exercise.p:
Check the presentation for errors. If you find one, circle it and describe the mistake in words.

	\frac{4xy}{12x^2 y^3}
	= \frac{4xy}{3xy^2 \cdot 4xy}
	= \frac{\cancel{4xy}}{3xy^2 \cdot \cancel{4xy}}
	= 3xy^2

Check the presentation for errors. If you find one, circle it and describe the mistake in words.

	\frac{20x^2}{5x^5}
	= \frac{4 \cdot 5x^2}{x^3 \cdot 5x^2}
	= \frac{4 \cdot \cancel{5x^2}}{x^3 \cdot \cancel{5x^2}}
	= 4x^3
